{"word":"H7582 - שָׁאָה - shâʼâh - shaw-aw' - Be desolate - பாழாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁאָה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be desolate / பாழாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பாழாகு, இரை, ஆச்சரியப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to crash, to make a din or to crash, to crash into ruins, to be in ruins, to be desolated"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to crash into ruins"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be ruined"},{"paragraph":"2) to crash"},{"paragraph":"3) to be left (a desolation)"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause to crash"},{"paragraph":"2) to cause to be desolated"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>rush</i>; by implication to <i>desolate: - </i>be desolate, (make a) rush (-ing), (lay) waste."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7582 - שָׁאָה - shâʼâh - shaw-aw'/7582\">H7582</a>, <a href=\"#/H7584 - שַׁאֲוָה - shaʼăvâh - shah-av-aw'/7584\">H7584</a>, <a href=\"#/H7588 - שָׁאֹון - shâʼôwn - shaw-one'/7588\">H7588</a>, <a href=\"#/H7591 - שְׁאִיָּה - shᵉʼîyâh - sheh-ee-yaw'/7591\">H7591</a>, <a href=\"#/H7612 - שֵׁאת - shêʼth - shayth/7612\">H7612</a>, <a href=\"#/H8351 - שֵׁת - shêth - shayth/8351\">H8351</a>"}]}